  1 by 1 by 1 MPI processor grid
create_atoms 1 box
Created 500 atoms
  using lattice units in orthogonal box = (0 0 0) to (20.124227 20.124227 20.124227)
  create_atoms CPU = 0.000 seconds
mass 1 1.0

# ── Potential ──
pair_style eam/alloy
pair_coeff * * Al_wkg_MSMSE_2009.set Al

# ── Variables ──
variable delta equal 0.000001
variable len0 equal lx

# ── Initial Minimization ──
thermo 100
min_style cg
minimize 1e-25 1e-25 50000 100000
